<p>SPY</p>
<p>explorator refers to a person sent out to scout out conditions in an enemy country.</p>
<p>speculator refers to real spies sent out to explore the intentions of the enemy as well as the prevailing enemy conditions.</p>
<p>emissarius refers to a person sent on a secret mission, secret negotiations or other secret transactions in enemy country.</p>
